Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:03.85,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:13.90,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}お互いのプライドを研ぎ澄ませよぜ
