Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:18.91,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}敞開任何言語之類的裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:28.33,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}相互碰撞 相互摩擦 rolling stone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:31.00,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}相遇是 shockwave shockwave
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:36.09,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}向未知的世界邁出腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:38.64,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}無謀的挑戰者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:43.98,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}只要用手中的刀劈開明天就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:46.06,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}這並不是別人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:49.86,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}是只屬於自己的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:55.82,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}因為我們都是未經琢磨的鑽石！
